title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 §§ 65-4.9 - Serving of notice
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 §§ 65-4.9 - Serving of notice

State Regulations

The IDA, the designated organization and the parties may use facsimile transmission, telex, telegram or other written or electronic forms of communication to give the notices required by this Subpart. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11
§§
65-4.9

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
